<p>Read and be willing to follow&nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/policies/policy1_4.htm" title="Guest speaker policy" target="_blank">University Policies and Procedures 1-4: Guest Speaker</a>. Potential speakers are not to be contacted until official approval has been received. &nbsp;</p>
<p>Download the&nbsp;<a href="Documents/university-relations/Forums/SpeakerRequest.pdf" target="_blank">Guest Speaker Request Form</a>. Please complete appropriate steps based on designated target audience; submit form to appropriate administrator at least giving minimum advance time prior to event.</p>
